      • copyAssociates

        public void copyAssociates(TaxaAssociation association)
        Copies associations in association to this instance of TaxaAssociation.

        May lead to contained (gene) taxa being associated with multiple containing (species) taxons. To avoid this, see copyAssociates(TaxaAssociation, boolean).

        Parameters:
        association - the association to copy.

      • copyAssociates

        public void copyAssociates(TaxaAssociation association,
                           boolean zeroAll)
        Copies associations in association to this instance of TaxaAssociation.
        Parameters:
        association - the association to copy.
        zeroAll - boolean indicating whether or not to zero all current associations before copying. If set to false, copying may result in contained (gene) taxa being associated with multiple containing (species) taxons.
